{"tid":682501,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人轉咗新工啲同事好冷漠 好掛住啲舊同事","createTime":"2018-05-29T02:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T13:43:56.000Z","uid":187039,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5312f36c4c4f3e14a91ae277109d35e03a9c33e0","tid":682501,"uid":187039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"其實我都轉咗工大半年 不過仍然好掛住舊工d同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班人年紀差唔多 好玩得埋 大家生日又會搞surprise 聖誕交換禮物大家都好有心機揀禮物俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日對住八個鐘 做野之外 無所不談 講下人生有咩目標 講下理想 講下腦細壞話 講下廢話又得 (份工唔算太忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 仲開心過讀U嗰時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家走咗都會成日聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n轉咗新工 工作性質類似 以為d人應該差唔多啦<br />\n點知個個都勁冷漠 可以一日都講唔到一句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (除咗早晨同公事上既野) <br />\n又勁唔歡迎新同事 會有人幫手叮飯盒 淨係唔叮新同事個飯盒 擺喺雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返咗成年工都唔知d同事住邊 食飯大家各自食<br />\n如果唔係呢度人工高d 又有升職前境 我係完全唔想轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有諗過 其實係咪咁樣先係正常香港辦公室文化 <br />\n可能我淨係grad咗幾年 無乜經驗 仲係好幼稚 <br />\n搵錢係重要 我都明<br />\n我之前可能只係好彩先遇到咁好既同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求點醒"},{"pid":"0426b0e7db9c42e2f123bdce4e554e7035b392ed","tid":682501,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:36:22.000Z","msg":"係咪啲mk工 u記 餐廳果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9246dd1fe9aa86eb446df1aa99b0d36882a052c","tid":682501,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"你係咪first impression比人感覺唔好， 又或者一開波有人已經打你毒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d41d12072b705c4100742d2eeed16e8e3adbeba","tid":682501,"uid":187039,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0426b0e7db9c42e2f123bdce4e554e7035b392ed","tid":682501,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:36:22.000Z","msg":"係咪啲mk工 u記 餐廳果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"唔係啦 兩份都係坐office<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb09f2f85cc49a5f67107405a98332324a59304","tid":682501,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"咁新公司既舊同事互相關係係點?"},{"pid":"1fbb32434812bba144b59154fa2155519ade50dd","tid":682501,"uid":187039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9246dd1fe9aa86eb446df1aa99b0d36882a052c","tid":682501,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"你係咪first impression比人感覺唔好， 又或者一開波有人已經打你毒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過佢哋好似對所有新同事都係咁"},{"pid":"bc9694a947cf5ea542db376fbaa819eea6f6a8be","tid":682501,"uid":187039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb09f2f85cc49a5f67107405a98332324a59304","tid":682501,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"咁新公司既舊同事互相關係係點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"有d做得耐既會自己一兩個小圈子咁<br />\n其他唔多講野 各自食飯 office靜到咳都唔敢大聲咳"},{"pid":"eb1e9095583be9b70a4113b8864267d518245374","tid":682501,"uid":18470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c587b12731c15d92b918e19c75da4f0a98b1036b","tid":682501,"uid":74629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc969